        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Gunsmith Excise Tax Simplification Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt a person who manufactures, produces, and imports fewer than 50 firearms per year from the firearms excise tax.<p>Treats persons considered as a single employer for certain special rule provisions as a single person for such exemption.]]></text>
      </summary>
